Under and awaiting orders at Harrisonburg, Va., and en route

to Department of California with recruits from New York City, N.Y.

from April 15, 1876 to May 21, 1876;

En route to and on duty at Camp Lowell, Arizona, from August

5, 1876 to August 10, 1877, during which time was on leave of

